{"tid":2355901,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【初選大搜捕】黃浩銘反駁打劫論 斥李桂華「似馬戲團」","createTime":"2021-01-06T12:04:27.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-06T13:57:12.000Z","uid":240362,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"38dbf8330c805fa78dd13b931d0284333d8d54a5","tid":2355901,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T12:04:27.000Z","msg":"（獨媒報導）警方今早以涉嫌違反《港區國安法》第22條「顛覆國家政權」罪拘捕53人，包括民主派初選參選人、發起人戴耀廷、民主動力召集人趙家賢，以及前立法會議員區諾軒。民主派下午召開跨黨派記者會，斥政府漠視市民投票權，全面與民意對抗。社民連主席黃浩銘嘲諷警務處國家安全處高級警司李桂華以「打劫」比喻初選，「有李桂華出現真係會變成馬戲團」。<br />\n<br />\n社民連主席黃浩銘稱，梁國雄及岑子杰均被捕，未知二人是否能如期保釋。他反駁李桂華以打劫比喻初選，強調《基本法》賦予議員權力，「政府俾咗張支票人民，民意代表入去銀行兌換張支票攞返啲錢嘅時候，你竟然話我係打劫？」。他又諷刺李桂華失職，「你見到警察會隔咗5個月後先去拉打劫啲賊㗎咩？」他更向警方「下戰書」，指自己是梁國雄及岑子杰的堅實支持者，「咁係咪犯法？你咪嚟囉。」<br />\n<br />\n對於李桂華指初選參選人不由分說否決議案，企圖癱瘓政府。黃浩銘則指社民連及民主黨均沒有簽署「墨落無悔堅定抗爭派立場聲明書」，「有啲根本冇簽，咁點解要拉？都係藉口同廢話，根本係政治搜捕。」他要求李桂華主動解釋，「乜嘢係非法行為？非法在於啲乜嘢？」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1080047\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1080047&d=dNeHxx%2FttK3%2FgpwSwFVImZKGII16X6EVRppoT8yKAsg%3D&h=4067c5e4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1080047&h=5f64a5f2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1080047</a>"},{"pid":"9651191217a81ef2ec03db0730d85a3305b20940","tid":2355901,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T12:07:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28ecc8be5afedf840e2d6c432b1265a941a9465b","tid":2355901,"uid":96439,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T12:08:25.000Z","msg":"村長<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5db5f8bd35a005b9bedbc59a53e1ceea65a72392","tid":2355901,"uid":74058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T12:09:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7b1cc95fca5cde2ad7215560783d65ef4921e33","tid":2355901,"uid":51752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T12:14:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ff5e3205b30c21ed56da1c171fe759e9e693d67","tid":2355901,"uid":51271,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T12:17:00.000Z","msg":"根本連支票都未有，就話你會開空頭支票"},{"pid":"07d188397b4303c76ea1a7fffefddd3ab1bc3570","tid":2355901,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T12:18:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc03f7c3ce6643a58a0775ecd07e8c3695b953d8","tid":2355901,"uid":13724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T12:18:23.000Z","msg":"根本即場記者已經要咁問"},{"pid":"1b67a37d7f805ab9581472a9b3d260de760db083","tid":2355901,"uid":305767,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T13:55:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a54bb3d6dfbb1de3d8af2e31cb3588d6d787be2f","tid":2355901,"uid":271513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T13:57:12.000Z","msg":"馬戲團入面無人理的小丑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}